data.text: @elsieclutterbuk This is #Midwinter - a set my mum bought her mum in the 60s I think. She used to save coupons and get them from Woolworths I believe. I now actively hunt it down at auctions. We have the tea set, coffee set and dinner service. Just adore it

@katylittlelady My lot are also all negative. Let's hope it stays that way.
Stay safe x
